 | Gulf/FL | Year-round | Repeated due to demand | Pink | Top seller - Painted Bunting | Passerina ciris | TX/SE | Spring/Summer | Repeated due to demand | Rainbow | Top seller Note: Species distributions/seasonality broadly reference Cornell Lab of Ornithology (All About Birds), Audubon Guide, ABA checklists; verify locally for precision. 7) SOP: Research → Design → Listing → Fulfillment Table: End-to-End SOP (click-by-click with Inputs/Outputs) Step | Action | Tool | Click-by-Click | Expected Input | Expected Output | QA/Notes 1 | Build Master Species/Concept List | Google Sheets | Create sheet > Tabs: Species, Concepts, Assets > Share | Seed list (50 species, 100 concepts) | Organized KB sheet | Use Cornell/Audubon links in notes 2 | Gather Reference + Rights | All About Birds/Audubon; Stock; Your Photos; AI | For each concept, paste 2–3 reference URLs; source CC-BY photos or generate AI | URLs or prompts | Folder of refs (Drive) | Avoid copyrighted art; add attribution if required 3 | Create Design Briefs | Google Docs | Template per design: audience, hook, palette, product, dimensions | Design brief fields | 100 briefs | Speeds creative 4 | Generate Artwork | Illustrator/Photoshop or AI (Midjourney/DALL·E) | AI: prompt > upscale > inpainting; Manual: build vectors; Export CMYK | Prompts, vectors, palettes | 300 DPI print files | Keep text ≥10pt (posters), ≥16pt (blankets) 5 | Mockups | Printify/Printful mockup gen or Smartmockups | Upload art > choose product > generate lifestyle + plain mockups | PNG art | 3–5 mockups per SKU | Include zoom detail shot for older buyers 6 | Listing Copy | Shopify/Etsy | Title formula: [Species/Hook] + [Product] + [Size/Material] + [Region] | Brief + specs | SEO title, bullets, long desc | Include insider terms sparingly; 6 bullets max 7 | Pricing | Spreadsheet | Set per product target margin ≥60% blended | COGS, fees | Price table | Round to charm pricing (e.g., $169) 8 | Launch | Storefront | Create collections: Woven Blankets, Warblers, Owls, Regionals, Gifts Under $"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=ff2bd166-cfd5-4fd8-94e9-f75f4cfa1045","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=ff2bd166-cfd5-4fd8-94e9-f75f4cfa1045"}]}]}]
